column2: SELECT t.thingid, t.ndetect,t.ra,t.dec,d.objid,p.mjd,p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z,  p.err_u,p.err_g,p.err_r,p.err_i,p.err_z into mydb.MyTable_#  from thingIndex AS t, dbo.fgetNearByObjEq(#,#,#) n      Right JOIN detectionindex AS d ON t.thingid = d.thingid  left JOIN photoobjall  AS p ON p.objid = d.objid  where p.objid = n.objid ORDER BY t.thingid ASC
